  "title": "ISic003657. I.Sicily inscription 003657",
  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag; edition source: <a href=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/4MCP2PVV\">https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/4MCP2PVV</a></div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  <span class=\"textpartnumber\" id=\"aba\">section a</span>  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"diva--interpretive\">  <a id=\"aa-l1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>Δ </span></div>  <span class=\"textpartnumber\" id=\"abb\">section b</span>  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"divb--interpretive\">  <a id=\"ab-l1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>Ε </span></div>  <span class=\"textpartnumber\" id=\"abc\">section c</span>  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"divc--interpretive\">  <a id=\"ac-l1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>Ν </span></div>  <span class=\"textpartnumber\" id=\"abd\">section d</span>  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"divd--interpretive\">  <a id=\"ad-l1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>Γ </span></div>  <span class=\"textpartnumber\" id=\"abe\">section e</span>  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"dive--interpretive\">  <a id=\"ae-l1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>⧖ </span></div>  <span class=\"textpartnumber\" id=\"abf\">section f</span>  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"divf--interpretive\">  <a id=\"af-l1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>Σ </span></div>  <span class=\"textpartnumber\" id=\"abg\">section g</span>  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"divg--interpretive\">  <a id=\"ag-l1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>Ι </span></div>  <span class=\"textpartnumber\" id=\"abh\">section h</span>  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"divh--interpretive\">  <a id=\"ah-l1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>Τ </span></div>  <span class=\"textpartnumber\" id=\"abi\">section i</span>  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"divi--interpretive\">  <a id=\"ai-l1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>sign, uninterpreted </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag; edition source: <a href=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/4MCP2PVV\">https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/4MCP2PVV</a></div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"textpartnumber\" id=\"aba\">section a</span><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"diva--diplomatic\"><a id=\"aa-l1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>Δ</span></div><span class=\"textpartnumber\" id=\"abb\">section b</span><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"divb--diplomatic\"><a id=\"ab-l1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>Ε</span></div><span class=\"textpartnumber\" id=\"abc\">section c</span><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"divc--diplomatic\"><a id=\"ac-l1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>Ν</span></div><span class=\"textpartnumber\" id=\"abd\">section d</span><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"divd--diplomatic\"><a id=\"ad-l1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>Γ</span></div><span class=\"textpartnumber\" id=\"abe\">section e</span><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"dive--diplomatic\"><a id=\"ae-l1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>⧖</span></div><span class=\"textpartnumber\" id=\"abf\">section f</span><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"divf--diplomatic\"><a id=\"af-l1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>Σ</span></div><span class=\"textpartnumber\" id=\"abg\">section g</span><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"divg--diplomatic\"><a id=\"ag-l1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>Ι</span></div><span class=\"textpartnumber\" id=\"abh\">section h</span><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"divh--diplomatic\"><a id=\"ah-l1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>Τ</span></div><span class=\"textpartnumber\" id=\"abi\">section i</span><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"divi--diplomatic\"><a id=\"ai-l1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>sign, uninterpreted</span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2><a href=\"ISic003657_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; Marconi 1926, fig.27\" src=\"ISic003657_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic003657.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; Marconi 1926, fig.27\" src=\"ISic003657-thumb.jpg\"></a></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span><span>Text based upon the apograph in Marconi 1926; Marconi presents several of the letters 'reversed', but given that the orientation of a mason's mark need not follow the final orientation of the stone, this does not seem significant</span></span>; </li><li><span class=\"e.1\">e.1: <span>The symbol has the form of an hourglass</span></span><br></li><li><span class=\"i.1\">i.1: <span>The symbol has the form of an incomplete (upper left) and open (at the waist) hourglass</span></span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2> translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\">  </p><p>  </p></div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>  </p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> Marconi NSA 1926 134-135 fig.27 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001392\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001392</a></li><li> Jeffery 1961 278 no.61 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000677\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000677</a></li><li> Jeffery Johnston 1990 278 no.61 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000678\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000678</a></li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"><p>Gamma of the curved c-shape; nu slanting and with longer initial stroke; sigma four barred and very open.</p> Line 1    Interlineation line 1 to 2    </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence.  </div>",
